                        <interp inst="t18350921-name-591" type="given" value="ESTHER"></interp>ESTHER DAWKINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the prosecutor's sister. I was coming out of the kitchen, and saw the prisoner with my brother's coat in his hand—I told my brother, who pursued him—the coat had hung at the bottom of the stairs with the shoes.</p>
